In a large bowl, beat cream cheese until fluffy. Gradually beat in EAGLE BRAND(R) until smooth. Stir in lemon juice and vanilla. Slice 2 bananas and dip in lemon juice and drain. Line bottom of crust with bananas and 2/3 of orange segments. Pour filling over fruit. Chill 3 hours or until set. Before serving, slice remaining banana; dip in lemon juice and drain. Garnish top with banana slices and remaining orange segments. Store leftovers covered in refrigerator.